snippet.title: I Can't Escape: Darkness - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Now Available: http://store.steampowered.com/app/346090
More Trailers: http://www.icantescape.com

Fancy Fish Games is here to help you survive I Can't Escape: Darkness!  The dungeon changes (procedurally) every time you play, and you are going to die!  Over and over!  And that's not bad!  Watch and learn!
